The paper focuses on data mining and graph sequences, which are common topics in the sub-category of cs.DM (Data Mining). The paper also deals with dynamic properties of data, which falls under the sub-category of cs.SI (Social and Information Networks). The algorithms presented in the paper have a polynomial delay, which is a common topic in the sub-category of cs.LG (Learning). The paper also deals with graph structures, which is a common topic in the sub-category of cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms). Finally, the paper deals with cliques and connected vertex subsets, which are common topics in the sub-category of cs.CC (Computational Complexity).
